{"tid":1804122,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"樂瞳性感谷戲笑談避年","createTime":"2019-12-30T17:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T08:08:03.000Z","uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2f1faee29d79a8f80059e6d8f9570cfe4b884e9a","tid":1804122,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T17:51:09.000Z","msg":"最後一個2019垃圾po <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LEMfr09.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLEMfr09.gif&h=68991de0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李璨琛和樂瞳出席電影《大盜演》友好首映場，主演該片兼擔任監製的李璨琛，表示該片預計於賀歲第二檔期上映，又認為賀歲檔期電影的對手很強，當中有西片、黃子華等，所以退為其次選擇第二檔期上映。談到上映時會否入戲院謝票，他表示優先場次也有現身謝票，觀眾反應幾好，若再次謝票可跟女兒Lucy同行到場，但不能入場睇戲，因為女兒對地方不熟悉會扭計。談到農曆年，他說會在港度過，笑言會出動女兒逗利是幫補一下。"},{"pid":"aea34d263e8e2c11bd1c3d5b3d745920ddc6b414","tid":1804122,"uid":44730,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T17:51:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191230/_2019123022544827631.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191230%2F_2019123022544827631.jpeg&h=31f14fbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a077df9708dc7db7922217b57f15b6a6c8f50bd4","tid":1804122,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T17:51:53.000Z","msg":"性感上陣造勢的樂瞳笑言，為免被追問幾時到她派利是，今年農曆年想外遊避年，又自爆曾被貌似韓國「小鮮肉」者「抄牌」，因當時好驚兼趕住上的士未有理會。在旁的李璨琛即笑說：「咁你都唔Like？結果咪無拖拍囉！」問到可有男生介紹畀樂瞳？他說：「等我個女啲朋友，睇下有冇適合，但樂瞳要等吓喎！」"},{"pid":"8fe9bb156e6c45764b757f21195f8498d637a45e","tid":1804122,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T17:51:54.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJp1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=80545140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ht